snippet: Vast quantities of work are for sale at the Frieze New York art fair, which is emblematic of the high-profile, high volume art-industrial economy.
abstract: Holland Cotter reviews the Frieze New York art fair on Randalls Island, which features works from nearly 180 art galleries.
